      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "An Icy Blade So Bright",
        "Client": "Hamon the Blacksmith",
        "Description": "I just don\u0027t understand young\r\nhunters and their \u0022fashion\u0022...\r\nSome of them even paint their glasses\r\nsolid black! It boggles the mind!\r\nWell, if this sort of thing interests\r\nyou, complete my request and I\u0027ll\r\ngive you the materials to make them.",
        "Target": "Hunt a Goss Harag",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Une lame glac\u00E9e \u00E9tincelante",
        "Client": "Hamon le forgeron",
        "Description": "Ah, les jeunes chasseurs et leur\r\n\u0022mode\u0022... Certains peignent\r\nm\u00EAme leurs lunettes en noir !\r\n\u00C7a me d\u00E9passe ! Enfin... Si ce\r\ngenre de trucs t\u0027int\u00E9resse,\r\noccupe-toi de ma requ\u00EAte et je\r\nte donnerai de quoi faire pareil.",
        "Target": "Chasser un Goss Harag",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Una lucente lama di ghiaccio",
        "Client": "Hamon il fabbro",
        "Description": "Alcuni giovani cacciatori\r\namano dipingere gli occhiali\r\ndi nero. Ma che moda \u00E8?! Non\r\nla capisco! Se ti piacciono\r\nqueste cose, completa la mia\r\nrichiesta e ti dar\u00F2 i materiali\r\nnecessari per crearli.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Goss Harag",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Eine leuchtende Eisklinge",
        "Client": "Hamon der Schmied",
        "Description": "Diese jungen J\u00E4ger und ihre\r\n\u0022Mode\u0022... Manche malen sogar\r\nihre Brille ganz schwarz an!\r\nVerwirrend! Aber falls dich\r\ndas interessiert, erf\u00FCll meine\r\nAnfrage, dann gebe ich dir die\r\nMaterialien daf\u00FCr.",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Goss Harag.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Fulgurante filo de hielo",
        "Client": "Hamon el herrero",
        "Description": "No entiendo la \u0022moda\u0022 de los\r\ncazadores j\u00F3venes... \u00A1Las gafas\r\nde algunos son completamente\r\nnegras! \u00BFQu\u00E9 sentido tiene?\r\nEn fin, si te interesan esas\r\ncosas, completa mi misi\u00F3n y\r\nte dar\u00E9 materiales para unas.",
        "Target": "Caza un Goss Harag",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u042F\u0440\u043A\u0438\u0439 \u043B\u0435\u0434\u044F\u043D\u043E\u0439 \u043A\u043B\u0438\u043D\u043E\u043A",
